snippet.title: Moon Jelly / Space Jelly Unreleased N64 game demo
snippet.description:
Video footage of the unreleased N64 game Space Jelly by Software Creations, also known as Moon Jelly.

I found this tape in my Dad's loft. I have no idea how I came to be in possession of it. It must have somehow followed me home from Psygnosis. I can only surmise that Software Creations had pitched it to Psygnosis for publishing.
